description: The 2023 music video for "BIG EVERYTHING" by Busta Rhymes, featuring DaBaby and T-Pain, showcases a dynamic collaboration among these artists. The video is part of Busta Rhymes' promotional efforts for his album "Blockbusta." In this collaboration, Busta Rhymes and DaBaby exchange verses over a beat reminiscent of classic hip-hop, with T-Pain adding his distinctive vocals to the mix. The video and song highlight the artists' lyrical prowess and their ability to create an engaging hip-hop track that appeals to fans across different eras of the genre.
